CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1957, pg. 12 reads: "The Frogs Entertain - The above pictures were taken at the Frogs' first affair during the club's 47th annual celebration of Frogs Week. Held Sunday at the Villa Monaco, members of the club entertained their wives and their out-of-town guests at a swank  cocktail party and buffet supper..."
TitMainTitle: Women selecting cold cuts from banquet spread in the Villa Monaco for the 47th Annual FROGS Week
